#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Pseudopod.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 7 (1d8 + 3) bludgeoning damage. If the mimic is in object "
"form, the target is subjected to its Adhesive trait.    \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"7 (1d8 + 3) piercing damage plus 4 (1d8) acid damage.\n"
msgstr ""
